                  Pioneering flavors and fragrances
                



                  A passion to co-create tastes and smells
                



                  Dedicated to innovations
                



                  Join us in our journey of discovery
                



                  Connect to IFF
                

















                          Pioneering sensorial experiences that move the world
                        

                              Explore IFF
                            

















              We are the catalyst for discoveries that spark the senses and transform the everyday 
            

We are always exploring and working tirelessly to discover flavors, fragrances, and cosmetic ingredients that inspire our customers and delight consumers.











                      Taste
                    


                        Discover how you taste what we do
                      














                              We are scientists of the senses
                            



Flavor is what gives food and drinks their magic and makes our sense of taste so precious. It is also the most important driver of food purchases, product loyalty, and demand from consumers. We deliver first-to-market, groundbreaking flavors and ingredients that push the boundaries of convention and help our customers delight consumers all over the world.



                                Explore
                              
















                      Smell
                    


                        Discover how you smell what we do
                      














                              We dare to dream - and are never content with the norm
                            



Scent is one of the most powerful influencers of human social interactions - and it is at the heart of our business. We regard fragrance as our passion - a place to explore and discover, so that we can continue to develop revolutionary fragrances and fragrance ingredients which will help our customers move consumers.



                                Explore
                              
















                      Touch
                    


                        Discover how you touch what we do
                      














                              We are in the business of discovery
                            



What if there was a new generation of beauty products that went further than ever before in enhancing the world of touch? What if cosmetics could include technologies that change the look, feel, and experience of our skin? We're determined to discover and continue to deliver cosmetic and personal care ingredients and solutions that are innovative.



                                Explore
                              

















                            We are scientists of the senses
                          



Flavor is what gives food and drinks their magic and makes our sense of taste so precious. It is also the most important driver of food purchases, product loyalty, and demand from consumers. We deliver first-to-market, groundbreaking flavors and ingredients that push the boundaries of convention and help our customers delight consumers all over the world.



                              Explore
                            













                            We dare to dream - and are never content with the norm
                          



Scent is one of the most powerful influencers of human social interactions - and it is at the heart of our business. We regard fragrance as our passion - a place to explore and discover, so that we can continue to develop revolutionary fragrances and fragrance ingredients which will help our customers move consumers.



                              Explore
                            













                            We are in the business of discovery
                          



What if there was a new generation of beauty products that went further than ever before in enhancing the world of touch? What if cosmetics could include technologies that change the look, feel, and experience of our skin? We're determined to discover and continue to deliver cosmetic and personal care ingredients and solutions that are innovative.



                              Explore
                            

















                    At the heart of IFF is our focus on forging new possibilities for a regenerative, healthy and abundant world.  
                  

                        See how IFF sustains
                      











                    At the heart of IFF is our focus on forging new possibilities for a regenerative, healthy and abundant world.  
                  

                        See how IFF sustains
                      











                          Pushing the boundaries of tomorrow
                        

For more than 128 years, we've been pioneers of the senses - and we never stop looking to the future. We create sense-sparking offerings in 13 subcategories, ranging from perfume, fragrance ingredients, and cosmetic actives to dairy, beverages, sweet, and savory flavors — co-creating 35,000 products annually. We're built on collective imagination, chemistry, consumer insights, and food technology - and the drive to push boundaries. Our mission: to deliver innovative "firsts", year after year.


                              Explore our vision 2020 strategy
                            












                  Pushing the boundaries of tomorrow
                

For more than 128 years, we've been pioneers of the senses - and we never stop looking to the future. We create sense-sparking offerings in 13 subcategories, ranging from perfume, fragrance ingredients, and cosmetic actives to dairy, beverages, sweet, and savory flavors — co-creating 35,000 products annually. We're built on collective imagination, chemistry, consumer insights, and food technology - and the drive to push boundaries. Our mission: to deliver innovative "firsts", year after year.


                      Explore our vision 2020 strategy
                    










                    Bring innovative ideas to life at IFF
                  

Our business is fueled by a sense of discovery: by constantly asking “what if?”
That passion for exploration drives our people to co-create unique scents, tastes, and tactile experiences. We never forget that we contribute to products that touch and enhance the lives of millions around the world at the fundamental level of sensation and emotion. Every day is an opportunity to make a difference.



7,400 Employees


S&P 500 Company


$3.1 Billion in Sales




                        Become a catalyst
                      














