                          Pushing the boundaries of tomorrow
                        

For more than 128 years, we've been pioneers of the senses - and we never stop looking to the future. We create sense-sparking offerings in 13 subcategories, ranging from perfume, fragrance ingredients, and cosmetic actives to dairy, beverages, sweet, and savory flavors — co-creating 35,000 products annually. We're built on collective imagination, chemistry, consumer insights, and food technology - and the drive to push boundaries. Our mission: to deliver innovative "firsts", year after year.


