                          Exploring the possibilities of taste in ways that consumers - and our customers - love
                        









Tastepoint













                        Sparking the senses through foods and beverages
                      


















                                  Refreshment
                                











Refreshment comes in many forms – from your first sip of piping hot coffee in the morning to the cool, refreshing drink at the end of a long hot day. We create flavors that spark consumers' senses, always seeking to improve on the best - and explore the new.















                                  Rich and Creamy
                                











From low fat, high protein breakfast smoothies and thick savory yogurt, to a rich, cold, ice cream treat, we bring flavor and sensation together in ways that make consumers smile.















                                  Sweet Indulgence
                                











'Sweet'... even the word feels indulgent! Whether you're celebrating with a chocolate treat or enjoying a slice of the cake your grandmother made, sweetness is a comforting pleasure for young and old alike. We're always exploring ways to put a sparkle on people's taste buds - and make indulgence everyday.















                                  Savor This!
                                











A bowl of rich steaming noodles... a handful of delicately roasted nuts... savory flavors fulfil you like no others. We explore new ways to bring savory tastes to life, whether through low-salt or rich umami taste -  combining science with consumer research to create flavors that excite as well as satisfy.

















Refreshment comes in many forms – from your first sip of piping hot coffee in the morning to the cool, refreshing drink at the end of a long hot day. We create flavors that spark consumers' senses, always seeking to improve on the best - and explore the new.








From low fat, high protein breakfast smoothies and thick savory yogurt, to a rich, cold, ice cream treat, we bring flavor and sensation together in ways that make consumers smile.








'Sweet'... even the word feels indulgent! Whether you're celebrating with a chocolate treat or enjoying a slice of the cake your grandmother made, sweetness is a comforting pleasure for young and old alike. We're always exploring ways to put a sparkle on people's taste buds - and make indulgence everyday.








A bowl of rich steaming noodles... a handful of delicately roasted nuts... savory flavors fulfil you like no others. We explore new ways to bring savory tastes to life, whether through low-salt or rich umami taste -  combining science with consumer research to create flavors that excite as well as satisfy.











                    Where We Explore
                  




Select Item


                	Creativity
                

                	Flavorist School
                

                	Culinary
                

                	Regulatory Expertise
                

                	Delivery Systems
                

                	Authenticity
                

                	Naturals
                

                	Health & Wellness
                

                	Strategic Insights
                







                        Creativity
                      



WHAT IF every food product hit the spot, seamlessly bringing you the flavors you love?
We understand the power of food to move, excite and satisfy, and IFF provides our customers with the expertise, tools and technologies that combine into a complete one-stop-shop solution – so that the foods consumers buy taste and feel just right.












                        Flavorist School
                      



WHAT IF you had a continuous pipeline of flavorist talent?
IFF provides the catalyst for innovation, creating the breakthroughs of today and making the discoveries of the future.












                        Culinary
                      



WHAT IF your innovations could draw on a creative combination of global culinary arts, married with cutting-edge flavor technology and food science?
IFF's research chefs bring fresh culinary insights and innovation through our CulinEssence® program.












                        Regulatory Expertise
                      



WHAT IF you had a trusted adviser to be your partner as you navigate the continuously evolving, and increasingly complex, regulatory landscape?
IFF partners with industry leaders to serve our customers’ brands today and in the future.












                        Delivery Systems
                      



WHAT IF the foods we love could have the power and excitement of flavors found in fresh ingredients – but which are often lost in traditional production?
IFF helps select and retain the flavor volatiles in great fresh ingredients, so consumers get the perfect taste.












                        Authenticity
                      



WHAT IF your favorite brand of food was made with you in mind – reflecting the food culture where you live and the flavors you love?
We craft products so that their flavors are not just strikingly authentic, but specifically selected to satisfy local palates.
IFF draws on experience, insights and modern technology to create unique taste experiences that spark the senses.












                        Naturals
                      



WHAT IF you could access a full portfolio of natural, suitable-for-organic flavors as well as botanicals and extracts?
With nature’s true tastes and aromas as a guide, IFF is helping to meet the changing consumer needs of health and wellness.












                        Health & Wellness
                      



WHAT IF the flavors we all love could come in foods that made us feel great?
What if we could buy foods that fit a healthy lifestyle while making no concessions on taste and excitement?
As an R&D powerhouse, IFF is always exploring new possibilities, listening to consumers' demands for health and wellness – and helping our customers quickly meet them.












                        Strategic Insights
                      



WHAT IF you could anticipate the future needs of consumers, so you could bring new and winning ideas to the marketplace sooner? Fueled by cutting-edge, innovative research tools, and a team of leading industry experts, we are the catalyst for discoveries.
















Meet Tastepoint





We have launched Tastepoint by IFF  – a new company designed to service the dynamic middle-market customer in North America. Tastepoint by IFF represents the merger of David Michael & Co. and Ottens Flavors, two esteemed companies with long histories in the industry and reputations for outstanding service and products.














