Company Summary
International Flavors & Fragrances Inc. is a creator and manufacturer of flavor and fragrance products used by other manufacturers to impart or improve flavor or fragrance in a wide variety of consumer products. Fragrance products are sold principally to manufacturers of perfumes, cosmetics, soaps and detergents, and flavor products to manufacturers of prepared foods, beverages, dairy foods, pharmaceuticals and confectionery products.   





 







